title: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
description: Bug 4121 - JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported JAR in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is displayed when overwriting the exported JAR file for the second time. This behavior was observed on PA (8/17/01 2:03:29 PM).
EB: The exported JAR file should not include itself.
SR:
To reproduce this issue: 
1. Open the project directory.
2. Export the project as a JAR file.
3. Save the exported JAR file in the same project directory.
4. Overwrite the exported JAR file.
5. Observe the out of sync message.
